We're not all that bad.

652
00:34:30,853 --> 00:34:31,437
你是知道的
You know that.

653
00:34:31,479 --> 00:34:32,689
我知道
I do.

654
00:34:33,356 --> 00:34:35,275
我们并没有谈论地球上的人们
We're not talking about
the people on Earth.

655
00:34:35,316 --> 00:34:39,737
我是在谈论我的探险队的每个成员
在这里, 亚特兰蒂斯
I'm talking about every member
of my expedition team here, in Atlantis,

656
00:34:39,779 --> 00:34:43,533
以及自从我们到这里之后碰到的朋友
就像, Teyla的人民
and I'm talking about the friends we've
met since coming here, like Teyla's people.

657
00:34:44,993 --> 00:34:47,579
那也包括你, 你自己也包括在内, Weir 博士
There are some among you,
yourself included, Dr. Weir

658
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:49,747
我知道 Athar 会张开双臂欢迎...
that I know Athar would
welcome with open arms...

659
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:52,166
不过是其他人
but there are others.

660
00:34:53,293 --> 00:34:55,795
我已经挑选了这个探险队中的每个人
I hand-picked every
member of this expedition,

661
00:34:55,837 --> 00:34:59,215
我知道 Teyla 对她自己的人民很有信心
and I know Teyla feels as
confident about her own people.

662
00:35:00,425 --> 00:35:01,384
我知道
I'm sure.

663
00:35:01,426 --> 00:35:04,095
在今天结束之前
这只是一个信任的问题
At the end of the day,
this is a matter of trust.

664
00:35:04,345 --> 00:35:05,221
是的
Yes.

665
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:07,765
是这样,  Weir 博士
It is, dr. Weir.

666
00:35:08,766 --> 00:35:12,103
你扫描到一些东西没有,  McKay博士?
Have your scans found
anything yet, Dr. McKay?

667
00:35:17,775 --> 00:35:19,110
事实上...
Actually...

668
00:35:21,237 --> 00:35:22,071
没有
no.

669
00:35:23,323 --> 00:35:24,657
这到底是什么?
What the hell is this?

670
00:35:24,699 --> 00:35:25,909
我很抱歉, 少校
I'm sorry, Major.

671
00:35:25,950 --> 00:35:28,536
我们有理由调查清楚...
There was cause for
legitimate concern as to...

672
00:35:28,578 --> 00:35:30,496
我跟我声称的是否相同
whether I was or not who I claimed to be.

673
00:35:31,247 --> 00:35:32,207
我很抱歉, Chaya.
I'm sorry, Chaya.

674
00:35:32,248 --> 00:35:34,167
我真诚地希望这没有伤害你
I honestly felt it would do no harm.

675
00:35:34,209 --> 00:35:36,211
不要道歉了, Elizabeth.
Stop apologizing, Elizabeth.

676
00:35:36,669 --> 00:35:37,629
她是怎么知道的?
How did she know?

677
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,463
McKay...
McKay...

678
00:35:38,504 --> 00:35:40,423
她是一个古人, 少校.
she's an ancient, Major.

679
00:35:40,465 --> 00:35:41,257
她是什么?
She's what?

680
00:35:41,841 --> 00:35:42,717
我是对的, 是么?
I'm right, aren't I?

681
00:35:43,259 --> 00:35:44,844
完美的健康, 那个能量武器
The perfect health, the energy weapon,

682
00:35:44,886 --> 00:35:45,845
她所具有的基因...
the fact that she has the gene...

683
00:35:45,887 --> 00:35:48,348
在逻辑上只有一个解释
it's the only logical explanation.

684
00:35:48,389 --> 00:35:50,808
你到底在说些什么?
What the hell are you talking about?

685
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:52,602
我只是不明白这种行为
I just don't understand the act.

686
00:35:52,644 --> 00:35:57,065
我的意思是, 你要知道我们实在不惜一切代价的
同你们交谈, 向你们学习
I mean, you must know we'd give just about
anything to talk to you, to learn from you.

687
00:35:57,982 --> 00:35:58,816
我的意思是, 到底是什么?
I mean, what is it?

688
00:35:58,858 --> 00:36:01,527
你要... 检查我们什么?
What, are you... checking us out?

689
00:36:02,195 --> 00:36:04,530
我渴望来到亚特兰蒂斯
I see that in my desire to come to Atlantis,

690
00:36:04,572 --> 00:36:06,241
你们已经把我揭示得太多了
I have revealed too much of myself.

691
00:36:06,282 --> 00:36:07,283
他是对的?
He's right?

692
00:36:07,367 --> 00:36:08,326
我说对了?
I'm right?

693
00:36:09,285 --> 00:36:11,204
我就是你们所称作的"古人"...
I am what you call an "Ancient"...

694
00:36:12,455 --> 00:36:15,833
而且事实上我也根本不能
向你们提供避难所...
and it is also true that I can
never offer your people sanctuary...

695
00:36:15,875 --> 00:36:19,295
不过我来这里的原因, 你们解释错了.
but you are wrong as to why I came here.

696
00:36:19,337 --> 00:36:20,880
你为什么来这里?
Why did you come here?

697
00:36:22,382 --> 00:36:23,174
你, John.
You, John.

698
00:36:25,510 --> 00:36:26,177
我?
Me?

699
00:36:26,219 --> 00:36:30,515
我孤独的生活了那么长时间
这时你邀请我来到亚特兰蒂斯, 我...
I have lived in solitude for so long that
when you asked me to come to Atlantis, I...

700
00:36:30,557 --> 00:36:32,475
噢, 我的天哪, 他是Kirk.
oh, my god, he is Kirk.

701
00:36:33,518 --> 00:36:35,353
这么说从来不是为了 ...
So this was never about, ...

702
00:36:38,898 --> 00:36:41,568
我们能够独自在这里呆会么?
could we just have a
moment to ourselves here?

703
00:36:41,609 --> 00:36:42,569
不行
No.

704
00:36:42,902 --> 00:36:44,320
没关系
That's all right.

705
00:36:44,362 --> 00:36:47,073
我已经在这里呆得够长了
I've stayed here long enough.

706
00:36:55,915 --> 00:36:56,958
来吧, Chaya.
Come on, Chaya.

707
00:36:57,542 --> 00:37:00,461
你和你的人民是我们来这里的首要原因
You and your people were the
reason we came here in the first place.

708
00:37:00,503 --> 00:37:02,881
我不能... 我不能...
I can't... I can't...

709
00:37:09,888 --> 00:37:10,555
不
no.

710
00:37:11,681 --> 00:37:12,807
这到底是什么?
What the hell was that?

711
00:37:14,350 --> 00:37:15,560
它们来了
They're coming for them.

712
00:37:16,728 --> 00:37:18,354
我不应该丢下他们
I should have never left them.

713
00:37:18,396 --> 00:37:19,898
发生什么了?
What's going on?

714
00:37:21,274 --> 00:37:22,108
我很抱歉, John.
I'm sorry, John.

715
00:37:44,839 --> 00:37:46,549
我要驾一艘飞船回到Proculis.
I'm taking a jumper back to Proculis.

716
00:37:47,050 --> 00:37:48,343
刚刚发生了什么?
What just happened?

717
00:37:48,885 --> 00:37:50,345
要想可以找出原因我们只有一种办法
There's only one way to find out.

718
00:37:51,012 --> 00:37:51,888
去吧
Go.

719
00:38:14,827 --> 00:38:16,496
少校, 你可知道那边会是什么情况?
Major, are you sure you
know what you're flying into?

720
00:38:16,746 --> 00:38:19,082
我敢确信幽灵正在袭击Chaya 的人民
I have a pretty good idea the
Wraith are attacking Chaya's people.

721
00:38:21,709 --> 00:38:24,087
只有一艘船, 你别指望能打败它们!
You can't hope to
defend them with one ship!

722
00:38:24,671 --> 00:38:25,755
我想我也没有必要
I don't think I'll have to.

723
00:39:04,752 --> 00:39:05,837
你来这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

724
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:06,963
我来帮你
I'm here to help you.

725
00:39:07,839 --> 00:39:08,506
帮我?
Help me?

726
00:39:08,548 --> 00:39:10,592
保护你的人民
To defend your people.

727
00:39:13,011 --> 00:39:13,553
离开
Leave.

728
00:39:15,221 --> 00:39:16,681
我会处理的
I will take care of this.

729
00:39:58,348 --> 00:39:59,557
是 "Chaya" 么...
Is it "Chaya"...

730
00:40:00,099 --> 00:40:01,976
或者是 "Athar"?
我只是很好奇
or "Athar"?
I'm just curious.

731
00:40:02,018 --> 00:40:03,853
当我是一个凡人时, 我住在这里
When I was mortal, I lived here.

732
00:40:04,437 --> 00:40:05,647
这是我的家
This was my home.

733
00:40:06,481 --> 00:40:09,484
当我们当中那些你们称之为古人的升天后
When those of us who
you call the ancients ascended,

734
00:40:09,525 --> 00:40:12,445
我们本应该抛弃我们的人类情节
we were supposed to
leave behind us all human ties.

735
00:40:12,487 --> 00:40:14,906
我们当中某些人发现这太困难了
Some of us found that difficult.

736
00:40:16,032 --> 00:40:18,201
所以你无法眼看着你的人民
So you couldn't
stand by and watch your people

737
00:40:18,243 --> 00:40:19,160
被幽灵清洗
而无动于衷
getting wiped out by the Wraith.

738
00:40:19,202 --> 00:40:22,330
当它们可怕的舰队接近时
我的心里就会非常不安
When their terrible fleet approached,
I lashed out with my mind

739
00:40:22,372 --> 00:40:23,998
只有一个念头, 把它们全部都消灭
and with a single thought,
destroyed them all.

740
00:40:24,874 --> 00:40:27,627
我同类中的其他人并不赞同这种干涉
The others of my kind did not
approve of such interference

741
00:40:27,669 --> 00:40:32,048
对有形事物的干涉
于是我就被放逐
with corporeal matters,
and so I was exiled.

742
00:40:33,007 --> 00:40:36,594
对我的惩罚就是无终止的保卫这个星球
My punishment was the
unending protection of this world.

743
00:40:42,350 --> 00:40:44,269
那究竟为什么要装扮成人类?
Why pretend to be human at all?

744
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:47,981
这样, 日积月累
我就可以走到人民中去
So that, time to time,
I may walk among the people,

745
00:40:48,022 --> 00:40:51,359
作为仁慈友好的灵魂而被它们所接受
know them as the good and kind souls they are.

746
00:40:51,401 --> 00:40:56,656
几千年来
我来到又离开了那些村庄
For thousands of years,
I have come and gone to the villages,

747
00:40:56,698 --> 00:40:59,242
不过呆得都很短, 一直没有附上任何人...
never staying too long
to get attached to anyone...

748
00:41:00,785 --> 00:41:02,078
直道我遇见了你
until I met you.

749
00:41:03,746 --> 00:41:06,833
这些年来, 我从来没有对以前所作的选择后悔过...
I have never regretted the
choice I made all of these years...

750
00:41:07,750 --> 00:41:08,668
直到现在
until now.

751
00:41:10,795 --> 00:41:13,840
我被允许保卫我的人民
不过仅限于我的人民
I am permitted to safeguard
my people, but my people only.

752
00:41:14,507 --> 00:41:16,050
这就是对我的惩罚
This is my punishment.

753
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:19,345
这就是它为什么被称之为惩罚
This is what makes it punishment.

754
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:23,766
如果你们的人来到这里寻求我的保护
If your people came
here for my protection,

755
00:41:23,808 --> 00:41:25,435
其他人就会阻止我
the others would stop me.

756
00:41:25,476 --> 00:41:27,186
你明白了么?
Do you understand?

757
00:41:27,228 --> 00:41:29,063
我无法帮助你们的人
I can never help your people.

758
00:41:32,358 --> 00:41:35,486
我想我不能如此轻松的走开
I'm not sure I'm willing
to walk away that easily,

759
00:41:35,528 --> 00:41:37,363
我也并不想在这里谈论个人问题
and I'm not just talking personally here,

760
00:41:37,405 --> 00:41:39,866
虽然这已经成为了事实...
although that's definitely part of it...

761
00:41:41,451 --> 00:41:43,953
我们仍然有很多东西可以向你们学习
there is so much more
we can learn from you.

762
00:41:43,995 --> 00:41:45,747
我不能, John.
I can't, John.

763
00:41:45,788 --> 00:41:47,540
其他人不会同意的
The others won't allow it.

764
00:41:47,582 --> 00:41:48,416
这只是...
That's just...

765
00:41:48,458 --> 00:41:50,543
他们最高的法则, 决不干涉
it is their highest law to never interfere.

766
00:41:51,711 --> 00:41:56,549
我被限制在这些法则中了
尽管我也很想帮助你
I am bound by those laws,
however much I wish to help you.

767
00:41:57,342 --> 00:41:59,385
如此, 那么, 我们不能...
So, uh, we can never...

768
00:41:59,427 --> 00:42:00,553
我不能离开
I can never leave.

769
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:04,182
好吧, 我可以到这里来看你
Well, I could come and visit.

770
00:42:07,685 --> 00:42:11,022
现在我正在挑逗一个其他的物种
Now I'm flirting with
somebody from another species.

771
00:42:11,064 --> 00:42:13,775
我们的差别并没有你所想象的那么大
We're not as different as you think.

772
00:42:13,816 --> 00:42:15,985
噢, 我想我们的差别比你想的要大
Oh, I think we're more
different than you think.

773
00:42:18,112 --> 00:42:19,239
我可以展示给你看
I can show you.

774
00:42:20,907 --> 00:42:21,616
展示给我看?
Show me?

775
00:42:22,408 --> 00:42:24,202
通过彼此之间的分享
By sharing each other.

776
00:42:24,869 --> 00:42:27,330
我们会像其他人一样, 相互了解对方
We will know each other
as well as anyone ever can.

777
00:42:27,372 --> 00:42:29,999
好吧
Okay.

778
00:42:30,041 --> 00:42:33,211
午夜之前我要把车送回去, 虽然
I've got to get the car
back by midnight, though.

779
00:42:34,170 --> 00:42:36,839
这只需要花一点时间
This will only take a few moments.

780
00:42:38,424 --> 00:42:40,385
闭上你的眼睛
Just close your eyes.

781
00:42:50,353 --> 00:42:53,064
这可真是酷阿...


This is cool...

